General.Name: HarbourVest Global Private Equity Ltd
General.Description: HarbourVest Global Private Equity Ltd. specializes in primary, secondary, and direct co-investments as well as fund of funds investments. For fund of funds investments, it prefers to invest in private equity funds and invests in HarbourVest funds. The fund seeks to provide long-term capital growth primarily through investments in private market assets.
General.Address: Ground Floor, Dorey Court, St Peter Port, Guernsey, GY1 2HT
